snippet.title: Moo Lander Demo Trailer PAX & EGX ( 2020 )
snippet.description:
Moo Lander is a 2D platformer game in which you fly a spaceship, sucking cows, fighting enemies, solving puzzles and entering alien worlds.


Wishlist Moo Lander or Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1080040/Moo_Lander/


PAX & EGX page at https://www.paxegx.com/games/moo-lander
More info at http://moolander.com/ 
PAX & EGX Tournament details at http://moolander.com/multiplayer-tournament-pax-egx/

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/moolander
Twitter: https://twitter.com/moolandergame
Instagram: http://instagram.com/moo.lander/
